    <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: February 10, 2026</p>

        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>CardTrackerAI ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application.</p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Card Images:</strong> Photos you take of trading cards for grading analysis. These images are processed by AI to provide grading estimates and are not stored on our servers after processing.</li>
            <li><strong>Card Data:</strong> Information about cards you add to your vault, including player names, card details, grades, and estimated values. This data is stored locally on your device.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> We may collect device type, operating system version, and app version for troubleshooting and improving our services.</li>
            <li><strong>Purchase Information:</strong> If you subscribe to premium features, payment processing is handled by Apple (App Store) or Google (Play Store). We do not store your payment card details.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide AI-powered card grading analysis</li>
            <li>To display your card collection and portfolio value</li>
            <li>To process in-app purchases and subscriptions</li>
            <li>To improve our grading algorithms and app features</li>
            <li>To respond to your inquiries and support requests</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data Storage & Security</h2>
        <p>Your card collection data is stored locally on your device. Card images sent for AI analysis are processed in real-time and are not permanently stored on our servers. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information.</p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>Our app uses the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Anthropic (Claude AI):</strong> For card image analysis and grading predictions.</li>
            <li><strong>RevenueCat:</strong> For subscription and purchase management.</li>
            <li><strong>Apple App Store / Google Play Store:</strong> For payment processing.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data stored in the app</li>
            <li>Delete your card collection data by uninstalling the app</li>
            <li>Opt out of analytics (if applicable)</li>
            <li>Request information about data we process</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our app is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy in the app and updating the "Last updated" date.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@cardtrackerai.com</p>
    </div>
